.P
Set \fIcolor\fR as the background color for parameter \fIn\fR\. See \fBCOLOR NAMES\fR\.
.
.TP
\fB\-\-attribute[n]=[name]\fR:

.
.P
Set \fIname\fR as the attribute for parameter \fIn\fR\. See \fBATTRIBUTE NAMES\fR\.
.
